id: pm-doxj
title: pm-cli post-v0.1 roadmap & living backlog
description: "Forward-looking roadmap milestone anchoring the open, living backlog for pm-cli beyond v0.1. Complements (does not duplicate) the closed PRD delivery milestones."
type: Milestone
status: open
priority: 0
tags[6]: backlog,context-management,living-map,pm-cli,post-v0.1,roadmap
