author: maintainer-agent
goal: project management = context management
objective: "Deliver a universal, fully-customizable PM tool whose baseline primitives (via the pm SDK) adapt to any project"
value: A discoverable forward backlog turns the tracker from a completed-work log into a living context map for humans and agents
why_now: Tracker had 902 items but zero open/forward work; pm context returned empty. This milestone seeds the forward layer.
body: "Vision: pm is a universal, agent-optimized, git-native project management CLI that ships PM primitives via an SDK so any project can fully customize and optimize it. Guiding principle: project management = context management. This milestone groups the post-v0.1 capability epics and their open backlog (surfaced by the 2026-05-31 ecosystem audit pm-w7f2). PRD post-v0.1 roadmap items (advanced search tuning, adapter optimization, sandbox API surface) live here as concrete, dedup-checked work."
